Description: Each PoW block credits exactly its author with one BlockReward; all nodes agree on canonical hashes and finalize the window.
Network: ./zombienet.toml
Creds: /tmp/zn-creds.cfg

# Wait for height >= 20 on alice, then verify every node has finalized
# >= 20 and agrees on canonical hash for #1..#20, then reconcile miner
# rewards from genesis to #20. ~20s/block, allow ~10 min wall time.
alice: js-script ./miner-reward-and-finality.js with "alice,bob,charlie,dave,20,15" return is 1 within 600 seconds
